Achievements.Description: Make sure your Chipmunk look stylish and buy up all the items for it!

Achievements.Name: A perfect performance
Achievements.Description: No one is as good as you. Get 5 Stars in a single song.

Achievements.Name: The Whole Story
Achievements.Description: Get to know the full story and complete Story mode.

Achievements.Name: It went a little like this...
Achievements.Description: Come along for the ride and complete a song in Story mode.
